, our results expand to arbitrary resolution\nand enable high level user control of appearance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Sep 2021 01:49:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Sep 2021 20:23:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-01"}
