ino flux. In the improved models, the protosolar molecular cloud\ncore is characterized by a primordial metallicity in the range 0.0127-0.0157\nand a helium mass fraction in the range 0.268-0.274. (abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Sep 2021 07:45:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-17"}
