variable is a monotonically decreasing function\nof n o. The results are robust, namely the asymptotic properties on the\nregulated variable hold also in presence of any uncertainties in the controlled\nplant not destroying closed-loop stability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Sep 2021 07:59:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-15"}
