tation values are shown\nto be corrected by regularization-dependent finite corrections arising from\ncontact terms associated to the equation of constraint.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Sep 2021 11:36:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Sep 2021 19:53:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-22"}
